column5: Hey guys, looking for some guitar players in the Hamilton area, someone to Jam with so I can learn a few new things.

try the open mike nite at the snooty fox on tuesdays - if they are still doing it.  hosted by a local self taught guy who puts on a good show. you can watch, chat, or bring your axe. the music selections are broad, so dont be afraid to play whatever you know.
A little brid wanted me to post this..  https://www.berkleemusic.com/vai-live
